## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of how market structures influence business strategies. Some sources may have a publication bias or may not be peer-reviewed, which could affect the reliability of the information. Additionally, the dynamic nature of market structures means that the impact on business strategies can evolve over time, necessitating continuous research and analysis.

